casebody.data:
B. W. Blount, Plaintiff in Error, v. J. W. Barwick, Defendant in Error. Hocker & Duval, for Plaintiff in Error. Circuit Court of Marion County; W. S. Bullock, Judge. August 16, 1909.

Judgment in favor of Defendant in Error.

Writ of error dismissed before the clerk on praecipe of counsel for plaintiff in error,
